# Mintlify to Fuma Migration Rules

## Component Mappings

### Cards and Card Groups
```mintlify
<CardGroup cols={2}>
  <Card
    title="Title"
    icon="icon-name"
    href="link">
    Content
  </Card>
</CardGroup>
```

```fuma
<Cards>
  <Card
    title="Title"
    icon={<Icon name="icon-name" />}
    href="link">
    Content
  </Card>
</Cards>
```

### Code Blocks
```mintlify
```js
code here
```
```

```fuma
<CodeBlock language="js">
code here
</CodeBlock>
```

### Accordions
```mintlify
<Accordion title="Title">
  Content
</Accordion>
```

```fuma
<Accordion>
  <AccordionItem title="Title">
    Content
  </AccordionItem>
</Accordion>
```

### Callouts
```mintlify
<Callout type="info">
  Content
</Callout>
```

```fuma
